OL,6,FIt also emerged that Manchester
OL,7,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,8,Fmanages the MRI, had declared a Level
OL,9,F5 patient safety incident ` the most
OL,10,Fserious category ` about aspects of
OL,11,Fhis care.
OL,13,FA pre-inquest review hearing was told
OL,14,Fthat level was downgraded as a
OL,15,Fsubsequent mortality review by the
OL,16,Fhospital had concluded his death was
OL,17,F"possibly avoidable but not very
OL,18,Flikely".
