OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,FIt was said Mr Campbell had been fit
OL,7,Fand well until around January 2024
OL,8,Fwhen he had a number of stays in
OL,9,Fhospital before his final admission to
OL,10,Fthe MRI from May of that year.
OL,12,FThe hearing was told he was treated at
OL,13,Fthe MRI for an initial six-and-half
OL,14,Fweeks before his later admission
OL,15,Fthere, with a three-day stay at
OL,16,FSalford Royal Hospital in between.
