OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe said: "This is a medically complex
OL,7,Finquest. Kevin was admitted for six
OL,8,Fand half weeks to Manchester Royal
OL,9,FInfirmary in the earlier period.
OL,11,F"No clear underlying cause for heart
OL,12,Ffailure was identified in that period.
OL,14,F"The family have questions about the
OL,15,Ffirst admission. In broad terms, how
OL,16,Fit was there was a six-and-a-half week
OL,17,Fadmission and no clear cause was
OL,18,Fidentified and whether there was an an
OL,19,Fearlier opportunity."
