OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,FZak Golombek, who is the area coroner
OL,7,Ffor Manchester, adjourned proceedings
OL,8,Funtil a full inquest hearing which
OL,9,Fwill take place on a date which is yet
OL,10,Fto be fixed.
OL,12,FA spokesman for Manchester University
OL,13,FNHS Foundation Trust said it does not
OL,14,Fcomment on ongoing inquests.
OL,16,FIn a long career Mr Campbell scored 59
OL,17,Fgoals in 224 games for Arsenal and,
OL,18,Falongside the 1990/91 league title, he
OL,19,Falso won the FA Cup, League Cup and
OL,20,FEuropean Cup Winners' Cup at Highbury.
