OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe spent three years at Nottingham
OL,7,FForest after joining them in 1995 and
OL,8,Fhad a one-season stop at Trabzonspor
OL,9,Fin Turkey before moving to Everton in
OL,10,F1999.
OL,12,FHe stayed at Everton until 2005, where
OL,13,Fhe spent time as captain under Walter
OL,14,FSmith, and ended his career with
OL,15,Fspells at West Brom and Cardiff.
OL,17,FMr Campbell worked in the media after
OL,18,Fhis playing career and was a member of
OL,19,Fthe Black Footballers Partnership,
OL,20,Fwhich works to increase the voice and
OL,21,Finfluence of black footballers.
